text.data-name: Thoughtworks India is an attractive destination for technical talent and hires the best
We set a high bar Forbes ranks us as the toughest technology consulting company to get into. Glassdoor rated us as the most difficult companies to interview
Our people are passionate about tech, knowledge and experience, while important, must be accompanied with a genuine passion for technology
Culture of collaboration Given our position as a leader in Distributed Agile, we ensure we hire people who foster a culture of collaboration

Innovation Everywhere - even in Hiring. Finding people with the unique blend of knowledge, experience and passion that we look for leads us to innovative hiring practices like Hackathons and Geek Nights.
High acceptance rates on offer for engineers (> 85%)
We lose thoughtworkers because they either start their own start-ups, or go to work for startups, or join product companies
Lowest attrition among digital services providers (~ 11%)
A lot of Thoughtworkers return back to work with us after doing a stint elsewhere
